•	Used drop_duplicates()
•	Ensured unique records
•	Applied forward fill method
•	Verified data consistency
Day 2: Data Transformation
•	Converted categorical variables
•	Standardized formats
Day 3: Feature Engineering
•	Created derived features if needed
•	Improved dataset usability
Day 4: Encoding and Validation
•	Used Label Encoding
•	Converted text to numeric
•	Rechecked dataset integrity
•	Ensured no missing values
Day 5: Saving Data
•	Saved processed dataset
•	Organized folder structure
•	Explanation and overview of week 2
 Outcome
